Key responsibilities:
- Experience in welding of stainless steel component and assembly parts
- Using grinder to smooth out, welds or part from work piece
- House-keeping of production floor
- Any other task assigned by supervisor or superior

Requirements:
- Experience in Arc welding
- Experience in welding of vacuum equipment will be an added advantage
- Experience in sheet metal work processes like cutting, welding, forming, rolling with production experience for mechanical products
- SPM/NTC/ITC/Diploma with relevant working experience
- Self-motivated with good interpersonal skills and team-work spirit